OL,3,CRugby legend Gerald Davies left
OL,4,C'humbled and moved' by knighthood
OL,6,FFormer Wales and British and Irish
OL,7,FLions player Gerald Davies said he was
OL,8,F"honoured" and "moved" to have
OL,9,Freceived a knighthood in the New Year
OL,10,FHonours.
OL,12,FThe 79-year-old is a legend in Welsh
OL,13,Frugby, serving as Welsh Rugby Union
OL,14,Fpresident for four years and being one
OL,15,Fof only a few former players to have
OL,16,Fwon three Grand Slams.
OL,18,FThe ex-winger has been recognised for
OL,19,Fservices to rugby union and voluntary
OL,20,Fand charitable service in Wales.
