OL,3,CRugby legend Gerald Davies left
OL,4,C'humbled and moved' by knighthood
OL,6,FAcross Sir Gerald's 12-year
OL,7,Finternational career he collected 20
OL,8,Ftouchdowns in 46 Tests for his country.
OL,10,FHis performances ranked him among
OL,11,FWales' top players, taking a place
OL,12,Falongside the likes of Gareth Edwards,
OL,13,FBarry John and JPR Williams as a great
OL,14,Fof the game.
OL,16,FHe also featured in five Tests for the
OL,17,FLions, including all four on the 1971
OL,18,FNew Zealand tour that remains the
OL,19,FLions' only Test series triumph
OL,20,Fagainst the All Blacks.
