OL,3,CRugby legend Gerald Davies left
OL,4,C'humbled and moved' by knighthood
OL,6,FIn club rugby he played for Cardiff,
OL,7,FLlanelli and London Welsh and after
OL,8,Fhis retirement he became a highly-
OL,9,Frespected administrator in the sport.
OL,11,FHe was Lions manager for the 2009 tour
OL,12,Fto South Africa and he was Welsh Rugby
OL,13,FUnion president between 2019 and 2023.
OL,15,F"It is an amazing honour," Sir Gerald
OL,16,Ftold the PA news agency.
OL,18,F"I am humbled by it and moved by the
OL,19,Fthought that somebody, somewhere, has
OL,20,Fthought it worthy of giving me that
OL,21,Fhonour.
