OL,3,CRugby legend Gerald Davies left
OL,4,C'humbled and moved' by knighthood
OL,6,F"With that in mind, you are always
OL,7,Faware in getting an honour like this
OL,8,Fof the enormous support you get from
OL,9,Fyour family ` my wife Cilla and
OL,10,Fchildren Emily and Ben.
OL,12,F"They are constantly at my side in
OL,13,Fgiving me support over the years. It
OL,14,Fis not something that you achieve
OL,15,Fentirely on your own.
OL,17,F"I thank those who have encouraged me
OL,18,Fover the years, the generosity and
OL,19,Fkindness of friends, colleagues and
OL,20,Fcountless others.
