OL,3,CRugby legend Gerald Davies left
OL,4,C'humbled and moved' by knighthood
OL,6,F"I feel very emotional about it. I am
OL,7,Fsurprised by it. Words are really
OL,8,Fquite inadequate to describe it. It
OL,9,Fcomes out of the blue. I was
OL,10,Fdumbstruck in many ways, but you don't
OL,11,Fachieve these things on your own."
OL,13,FSir Gerald was made a CBE in 2003 and
OL,14,Fhis work off the rugby field also won
OL,15,Fhim many admirers.
OL,17,F"I have supported charities in the
OL,18,Fcommunities, and I have done so
OL,19,Fthroughout my life. I think that is
OL,20,Fimportant," he added.
